Tools for validating OSM public transport relations

Used by https://osm.kesto.de/routes/

Install required Python modules:
apt install python3-mako python3-simplejson

Fetch data from Overpass-API:
./fetch_overpass_data.py overpass_queries/ data/

Adjust output_dir in osmconfig.py to your needs.

Start overview generation script with profile "berlin_oepnv":
./generate.py berlin_oepnv
